name: Johnny Edmonston
description: m a friendly, easy going, not pretentious or materalistic, just a realist, not out to impress just be myself, an ordinary guy who loves kids. and animals (enjoy my walks along frankston foreshore with my king charles pup), I enjoy intelligent conversation over a coffee or wine, enjoy a good laugh, communicating with people and am the first to put my hand up if someone needs help hence my volunteering for the homeless. I love taking off for the day/weekend (anywhere in victoria) going to the city to visit museums, art galleries, I like being out in nature, exploring historic, natural wonders or spending time at country markets, footy, soccer, eating out for dinner (any crusine) with a nice bottle of wine. I love seeing a good movie (drama,action to chick flicks).I enjoy cooking, relaxing in the garden and listening to music (anything in between opera and that head banging crap). I enjoy going out with friends or just staying home listening to music, watching a dvd or just chillin out.
